<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>ترجمه الحافظُ في <span style="color:#950000">"اللسان"</span> <span style="color:#008000">(٥/ ٣٨٩)</span>.<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
